<ab facs="#facs_293_r1l4">ewrs <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd begert / daʒ vvir Jm geleitt cʒü vns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_293_r1l5"> <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc . 
<del rend="strikethrough">Alſo wöllen wir <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Andr<ex>res</ex></expan> <expan>Lampr<ex>echt</ex></expan></del> Das wöllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_293_r1l6">wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tun / Alſo wenn derſelb Andres Lamprecht cʒü vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_293_r1l7"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſant Jacobs tag nu ſchirſt / So ſol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_293_r1l8">er 
